    <abstract>
      <t>This document discusses the framework of supporting application-
   specific multicast traffic, i.e. multicast traffic other than
   ARP/ND, in a network that uses Network Virtualization using Overlays
   over Layer 3 (NVO3). It describes the various mechanisms and
   considerations that can be used for delivering such traffic.</t>
